# 强制所有文本文件使用 Linux (LF) 换行，防止 Docker/VPS 报错
* text=auto eol=lf

# 只有 Windows 脚本保留 CRLF
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# 二进制文件保护 (APK, 密钥, 图片) - 绝对不让 Git 修改
*.apk binary
*.aab binary
*.jar binary
*.keystore binary
*.jks binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary